AccessibilityLabel_Desc: The label to add to the table aria description
AllowFreeText_Desc: 'Allow free text mode' allows freetext entry with resolving to a suggestion
AutoHeight_Desc: The height that the control grows to when the tags do not fit the width available
Error_Desc: True if the control is in an error state
HintText_Desc: The text to display when no text input is provided
InputEvent_Desc: Signals an event - add a random element to make each event unique
MaxTags_Desc: The maximum number of tags that can be added
MinimumSearchTermLength_Desc: The minimum number of characters that must be entered before a suggestion search is performed
NoSuggestionFoundMessage_Desc: The message to display when no suggestions match the search term
Picker_Desc: Allows picking string tags from one dataset and adding to another
SearchTerm_Desc: The search term entered that should be used when filtering suggestions
SearchTermToShortMessage_Desc: The message to display if the search term is less than the 'Minimum Search Term Length' parameter - e.g. 'Keep typing'
SuggestionDisplayName_Desc: The column to use as the suggestions line 1
SuggestionSubDisplayName_Desc: The column to use as the suggestions line 2
TagDisplayName_Desc: The name of the tag aded or removed
TagError_Desc: Set to true to indicate an error on the added tag
TagKey_Desc: The key of the tag that raise the event
TagMaxWidth_Desc: The maximum width that tags can grow to before the text is truncated
TagsDisplayName_Desc: The column to use as the tag display name
